                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="card-footer">
                    <a href="https://www.booking.com/searchresults.html?ss=Alporchinhos,%20Portugal&checkin_monthday=9&checkin_month=10&checkin_year=2019&checkout_monthday=12&checkout_month=10&checkout_year=2019" target="_blank" class="card-link">
